Company Overview of M Fund, Inc. - M International Equity Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
M Fund, Inc. - M International Equity Fund is an open-ended variable annuity equity mutual fund launched and managed by M Financial Investment Advisers, Inc. The fund is co-managed by Northern Cross, LLC. It invests in the public equity markets of countries across the globe, excluding the United States. The fund invests in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in stocks of companies with market capitalizations of $1 billion or more. The fund invests also in preferred stock, securities that are convertible into common stock, American Depositary Receipts, European Depositary Receipts, International Depositary Receipts or Global Depositary Receipts. It benchmarks ...
M Fund, Inc. - M International Equity Fund is an open-ended variable annuity equity mutual fund launched and managed by M Financial Investment Advisers, Inc. The fund is co-managed by Northern Cross, LLC. It invests in the public equity markets of countries across the globe, excluding the United States. The fund invests in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in stocks of companies with market capitalizations of $1 billion or more. The fund invests also in preferred stock, securities that are convertible into common stock, American Depositary Receipts, European Depositary Receipts, International Depositary Receipts or Global Depositary Receipts. It benchmarks the performance its portfolio against the MSCI AC World ex US Index. The fund was formerly known as M Fund, Inc. - Brandes International Equity Fund. M Fund, Inc. - M International Equity Fund was formed on January 4, 1996 and is domiciled in United States.
Detailed Description


