M Fund, Inc. - M Large Cap Value Fund: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 25, 2017 11:43 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of M Fund, Inc. - M Large Cap Value Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
M Fund, Inc. - M Large Cap Value Fund is an open-ended variable annuity equity mutual fund launched and managed by M Financial Investment Advisers, Inc. It is co-managed by Aronson+Johnson+Ortiz, LP. The fund primarily invests in the public equity markets of the United States. It seeks to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in value stocks of large-cap companies with market capitalizations of $5 billion or more. It employs quantitative analysis with a focus on factors such as well-managed companies with quality cash profits, relatively low market valuations, positive price and earnings momentum, and favorable investor sentiment to create its p...
M Fund, Inc. - M Large Cap Value Fund is an open-ended variable annuity equity mutual fund launched and managed by M Financial Investment Advisers, Inc. It is co-managed by Aronson+Johnson+Ortiz, LP. The fund primarily invests in the public equity markets of the United States. It seeks to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in value stocks of large-cap companies with market capitalizations of $5 billion or more. It employs quantitative analysis with a focus on factors such as well-managed companies with quality cash profits, relatively low market valuations, positive price and earnings momentum, and favorable investor sentiment to create its portfolio. The fund benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the Russell 1000 Value Index. It was formerly known as M Fund, Inc. - Business Opportunity Value Fund. M Fund, Inc. - M Large Cap Value Fund was formed on January 4, 1996 and is domiciled in the United States
Detailed Description


M Financial Plaza1125 North West Couch StreetSuite 900Portland, OR 97209United StatesFounded in 1996



Phone: 503-232-6960

Fax: 503-238-1621








